These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, tram, skateboard, roller
4 different pets are kept: dog, fish, rat, pony
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
5. the person driving the roller is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Transport          | roller | skateboard | tram | jet-ski   |
| Pet   | fish  | dog     | rat   | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, journalist, doctor, nurse
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, frog, goldfish, snake
1. the nurse is the owner of the frog##1
2. the coach is on the far right##1
3. the journalist is on the right of the nurse##1
4. the nurse is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Job   | doctor | nurse | journalist | coach    |
| Pet   | goldfish    | frog      | hedgehog | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, plum, cranberry, raspberry
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, pakistani, british, turkish
1. the british is on the left of the turkish##1
2. the person eating avocado is the japanese##1
3. the pakistani is on the far right##1
4. the turkish is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
5. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Food         | avocado | raspberry | cranberry   | plum |
| Nationality   | japanese   | british | turkish | pakistani         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, motorbike, airplane, ship
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, old-henry, bluemaster, ritmeester
1. the old-henry-smoker is the person driving the ship##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
5. the blend-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Transport   | ship | motorbike | snowmobile  | airplane      |
| Cigar         | old-henry | ritmeester   | bluemaster | blend |

