.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, fanta, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, project-manager, teacher, firefighter
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the teacher is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the firefighter##1
4. the project-manager is on the right of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | fanta | 7up | hot-chocolate |
| Job    | fisherman       | firefighter | teacher | project-manager     |

