.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, disaster, horror, western
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, dahlia, daisy, sunflower
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
4. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | western | horror | spy | disaster |
| Flower           | rose      | daisy | sunflower | dahlia    |

