.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, ship, taxi, subway
4 different games are played: billiard, mah-jongg, chess, domino
1. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Transport   | taxi | ship | van | subway  |
| Game           | chess | billiard | domino       | mah-jongg |

