.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, pink, emerald, chestnut
House: craftsman, colonial, modern, farmhouse
1. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
2. the farmhouse house is the person who likes chestnut##1
3. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
4. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the colonial house##1
5. the craftsman house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Color         | emerald | blood-red      | pink | chestnut |
| House   | craftsman          | colonial | modern     | farmhouse    |

