.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, orange, lime, apricot
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, davidoff, chaman, swisher
1. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
2. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
3. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
5. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person eating lime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Food   | orange    | lime       | artichoke | apricot   |
| Cigar     | davidoff | chaman | swisher   | old-henry |

