.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, raspberry, banana, carrot
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, swimming, lacrosse, cycling
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
2. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Food    | cucumber | banana  | raspberry | carrot |
| Sport   | cycling | lacrosse | swimming          | weightlifting    |

