.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, alhambra, prince, dunhill
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, dancing, magic-tricks, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
4. the prince-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Cigar      | prince | alhambra  | baccarat | dunhill |
| Hobby   | video-games  | magic-tricks | hiking           | dancing   |

