2. the videographer is on the right of the librarian##1
3. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the accountant is on the right of the architect##1
5. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Job   | architect | accountant | librarian | videographer  |
| Movie-Genre           | epic | satire      | spy | drama |

