4 different games are played: go, scrabble, bridge, snooker
1. the person playing snooker is the person driving the roller##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is the person playing bridge##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
5. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Transport   | jet-ski | skateboard  | roller | airplane   |
| Game        | bridge | scrabble | snooker    | go |

