.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-16::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, orange, ivory, white
City: new-york, colone, nizza, venice
1. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
2. the person who likes brown is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
4. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who likes white##1
5. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4        |
| Color           | brown | white    | orange    | ivory |
| City   | colone      | nizza | new-york | venice       |

