The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, poppy, iris, tulip
1. the person who growstulip is the person traveling to boston##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is the person who growspoppy##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| City   | san-francisco      | boston | venice | hannover |
| Flower     | zinnia | tulip    | iris  | poppy |

