.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-18::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, soul, hip-hop, pop
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, march, november, may
1. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the fan of pop##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the fan of soul is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre      | d&b   | pop | soul   | hip-hop      |
| Birthday   | december | may      | march | november |

