.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, lemonade, coffee
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, doctor, scientist, security-guard
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the security-guard is on the left of the scientist##1
3. the scientist is the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the scientist is on the left of the lawyer##1
5. the lawyer is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage         | soy-milk | lemonade | coffee | water |
| Job   | security-guard     | scientist    | lawyer      | doctor   |

