.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
House: cape-cod, futuristic, palace, farmhouse
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, milk, sprite, fanta
1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the futuristic house##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the left of the palace house##1
4. the farmhouse house is the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| House   | cape-cod | palace | futuristic | farmhouse   |
| Beverage     | sprite  | tea    | milk       | fanta |

 